abstract: New medals are issued for Syracuse Ironman winners because original medals featured image of downtown Rochester.
lead_paragraph: Athletes who finished last week’s Ironman event through the Syracuse area will get a second medal because the ones they were initially given featured an image of the skyline of downtown Rochester.

headline.main: Medal Trouble at Ironman Event in Syracuse
